    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-07-28T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-07-28T19:00:00-05:00" n="578"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d578">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">839.00/7–2847: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Norweb</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">us urgent</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-07-28T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >July 28, 1947—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>411. President Grau late this afternoon informed me that energetic measures are
                    being taken to suffocate revolutionary activity based on <pb facs="0664" n="648"
                        xml:id="pg_648"/> Cuban soil and directed against Dominican Republic which
                    has been subject recent telegrams. He further declared public statement this
                    effect will be issued and subsequent ones as situation warrants.</p>
                <p>Inform War and Navy.</p>
                <p>Sent Department 411, repeated Ciudad Trujillo and Port-au-Prince.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Norweb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
